

Great! Here's a complete CSS-based portfolio example. This version includes HTML + external CSS to give you a clean and responsive design using just HTML and CSS.


---

ðŸŽ¨ Step 1: index.html

Create a file called index.html:

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>My Portfolio</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <h1>Your Name</h1>
    <nav>
      <a href="#about">About</a>
      <a href="#projects">Projects</a>
      <a href="#skills">Skills</a>
      <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section id="about">
    <h2>About Me</h2>
    <p>Hello! I'm a web developer passionate about clean design and great user experiences.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="projects">
    <h2>Projects</h2>
    <div class="project-card">
      <h3>Portfolio Website</h3>
      <p>A personal portfolio to showcase my work and skills.</p>
      <a href="#">View Project</a>
    </div>
    <div class="project-card">
      <h3>Blog Platform</h3>
      <p>A simple blog using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.</p>
      <a href="#">View Project</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="skills">
    <h2>Skills</h2>
    <ul class="skills-list">
      <li>HTML</li>
      <li>CSS</li>
      <li>JavaScript</li>
      <li>React</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section id="contact">
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Email: <a href="mailto:you@example.com">you@example.com</a></p>
    <p>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/yourusername">yourusername</a></p>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 Your Name</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>


---

ðŸŽ¨ Step 2: style.css

Create a file called style.css:

/* Reset some default browser styles */
* {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
  font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
  line-height: 1.6;
  background-color: #f8f9fa;
  color: #333;
}

header {
  background-color: #343a40;
  color: white;
  padding: 20px 0;
  text-align: center;
}

nav a {
  color: white;
  margin: 0 15px;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: bold;
}

nav a:hover {
  text-decoration: underline;
}

section {
  padding: 40px 20px;
  max-width: 900px;
  margin: auto;
}

h2 {
  border-bottom: 2px solid #ccc;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  padding-bottom: 10px;
}

.project-card {
  background: white;
  padding: 20px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

.project-card a {
  display: inline-block;
  margin-top: 10px;
  color: #007BFF;
  text-decoration: none;
}

.project-card a:hover {
  text-decoration: underline;
}

.skills-list {
  list-style: none;
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 10px;
}

.skills-list li {
  background: #007BFF;
  color: white;
  padding: 10px 15px;
  border-radius: 5px;
}

footer {
  background-color: #343a40;
  color: white;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 20px 0;
  margin-top: 40px;
}

/* Responsive */
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .skills-list {
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: start;
  }

  nav a {
    display: block;
    margin: 10px 0;
  }
}

